05/27/86 opened_database, odb

Syntax as an active request: [odb {path}]


Function: returns true if there is an open database and false if
there isn't.  This active request returns true if path is
supplied and it is the mrds database that is currently open,
false is returned if it is not the opened database.


Arguments:
path
   the pathname of a MRDS database or of a data submodel
   associated with a MRDS database.
